{File:PLTR_IS.txt  Index:1  Index Date:20250509  PL:100.00%  PS:0%  Trades:4  CL:0}

IF HIGH OF 1 BARS AGO > HIGH OF 0 BARS AGO
AND HIGH OF 0 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 1 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 1 BARS AGO > OPEN OF 0 BARS AGO
AND OPEN OF 0 BARS AGO > CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO
AND CLOSE OF 0 BARS AGO > LOW OF 0 BARS AGO
AND LOW OF 0 BARS AGO > OPEN OF 1 BARS AGO
AND OPEN OF 1 BARS AGO > LOW OF 1 BARS AGO
THEN BUY NEXT BAR ON THE OPEN WITH
PROFIT TARGET AT ENTRY PRICE + 3.7828797 %
AND STOP LOSS AT ENTRY PRICE - 3.7828797 %
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
